      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="32cbb7fc9177a802" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Cruelty: When you use force, you can choose to maim or deliver painful injuries to draw out your foe’s suffering. Whenever you inflict damage, you can choose to inflict 2 fewer points of damage to ease your next attack against that foe.</source>
        <target></target>
        <context-group name="" purpose="location">
