      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="14219a0709fd7590" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Skill: You’re trained in tasks related to deception, intimidation, and persuasion when you interact with characters experiencing physical or emotional pain.</source>
